metadata.name: Tangerine Abyss
metadata.description:
A place of solitude where the fierce soul finds peace and the guarded heart finds sleep.

--

This piece was created using an iterative back-and-forth process capturing and curating raw synthographs using very specific prompt engineering techniques on custom and pre-trained (Midjourney) AI models.

It was further refined using Photoshop to experiment with colors and compositions, to paint over, collage or mask initial images in order to accentuate or reveal the stylistic aspects of the main subject I have chosen.
